ed nephropathy.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/192931/', '', 'Tamsulosin, Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Metronidazole, Simeprevir, Rosuvastatin, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Clindamycin, Ciclopirox, More', 'Ethiodized oil, Iopanoic acid, Tyropanoic acid, Iopodic acid', 1767369485);
